        $('#myModal').fadeIn();

 <script type="text/javascript">
        function edit_costbasis(divbasis_id)
        {
            document.getElementById('displaybasisdiv_'+divbasis_id).style.display='none';
            document.getElementById('displaybasisi1div_'+divbasis_id).style.display='none';
            document.getElementById('editbasisdiv_'+divbasis_id).style.display='';
        }
        
        function update_costbasis(basis_symb)
        {
            var basisval=document.getElementById('edtbasisval_'+basis_symb).value;
            if(basisval=='')
            {
                alert("Please enter value in Cost Basis to continue");
                return false;
            }

            if(basisval!='')
            {
                 var basisspecialcharacters=check_specialcharacters(basisval,'Cost Basis');
                 if(basisspecialcharacters=="false")
                 {
                     alert("Please remove Special characters like !'#%"+'"'+"&=\|/ from Cost Basis to continue.");
                     return false;
                 }
                 var basisnumber_validation=number_validation(basisval,'Cost Basis');
                 if(basisnumber_validation=="false")
                 {
                     alert("Please removed the word from Cost Basis text to continue.");
                     return false;
                 }
                 
                 projected_formsubmit();
            }
        }
        
        function edit_shares(div_id)
        {
            document.getElementById('displaysharesdiv_'+div_id).style.display='none';
            document.getElementById('displayshares1div_'+div_id).style.display='none';
            document.getElementById('editsharesdiv_'+div_id).style.display='';
        }
        
        function update_sharesval(div_symb)
        {
            var txt_val=document.getElementById('edtsharesval_'+div_symb).value;
            if(txt_val=='')
            {
                alert("Please enter value in # of Shares to continue");
                return false;
            }

            if(txt_val!='')
            {
                 var sharesspecialcharacters=check_specialcharacters(txt_val,'# Of Shares');
                 if(sharesspecialcharacters=="false")
                 {
                     alert("Please remove Special characters like !'#%"+'"'+"&=\|/ from # Of Shares to continue.");
                     return false;
                 }
                 var sharesnumber_validation=number_validation(txt_val,'# Of Shares');
                 if(sharesnumber_validation=="false")
                 {
                     alert("Please removed the word from # Of Shares text to continue.");
                     return false;
                 }
                 
                 projected_formsubmit();
             }
        }
        
        function check_datecquired(date_val)
        {
			//alert('lifestyle');
            projected_formsubmit();
        }
        
        function edit_1yrgrowth(div_id)
        {
            document.getElementById('display_1yrgrowthdiv_'+div_id).style.display='none';
            document.getElementById('display_1yrgrowth1div_'+div_id).style.display='none';
            document.getElementById('edit_1yrgrowthdiv_'+div_id).style.display='';
        }
        
        function update_1yrgrowth(div_symb)
        {
            var txt_val=document.getElementById('edt_1yrgrowthval_'+div_symb).value;

            var sharesspecialcharacters=check_specialcharacters(txt_val,'Dividend 1 Yr growth');
            if(sharesspecialcharacters=="false")
            {
                alert("Please remove Special characters like !'#%"+'"'+"&=\|/ from Dividend 1 Yr growth to continue.");
                return false;
            }
            var div_growhnumber_validation=number_validation(txt_val,'Dividend 1 Yr growth');
            if(div_growhnumber_validation=="false")
            {
                alert("Please removed the word from Dividend 1 Yr growth text to continue.");
                return false;
            }
            
            projected_formsubmit();
            
        }
        
        function reset_1yrgrowth(div_symb)
        {
            document.getElementById('edt_1yrgrowthval_'+div_symb).value='0.0';
            update_1yrgrowth(div_symb);
        }
        
        function check_specialcharacters(name,tagname)
        {
            var iChars = "#%"+'"'+"&'\\\/|\!";
                for (var i = 0; i <name.length; i++)
                {
                    if (iChars.indexOf(name.charAt(i)) != -1)
                    {
                        return "false";
                    }
                }
        }
        function number_validation(name,tagname)
        {
                var iChars = /^[a-zA-Z]+$/;
                for (var i = 0; i < name.length; i++)
                {
                    if(iChars.test(name.charAt(i)))
                    {
                        return "false";
                    }
                }
        }
        function projected_formsubmit()
        {
            document.formgo.submit() ;
        }
		
		
		
    </script>

                            <h2 style='color:white'>Chatham Lodging Trust ( NYSE : <a href="/dividend-quote/cldt/">CLDT</a> )</h2>                                                            <p style="color: white; font-size: 12px;"> Chatham Lodging Trust is a real estate investment trust (REIT). All of Co.'s assets are held by, and all operations are conducted via its operating partnership, Chatham Lodging, L.P., which leases Co.'s wholly owned hotels to taxable REIT subsidiary lessees. Co.'s wholly owned hotels include hotels that operate under the Residence Inn by Marriott brand and Homewood Suites by Hilton brand, as well as hotels that operate under the Courtyard by Marriott brand, the Hampton Inn or Hampton Inn and Suites by Hilton brand, the Hilton Garden Inn by Hilton brand, the SpringHill Suites by Marriott brand, the Hyatt Place brand and all suite hotels that operate under the Embassy Suites brand. </p>
